ROWA GROUP Holding GmbH
ROWA GROUP: A strong community sets standards for polymer materials

With more than 60 years of experience in the plastics industry, the ROWA GROUP consists of powerful partners: ROMIRA (engineering plastics and blends), ROWA Masterbatch (color, additive and combination masterbatches), ROWASOL (liquid colors and additives, dosing systems), ROWA Lack (coating systems, top coats and mono-pigment preparations), and TRAMACO (chemical blowing agents and adhesion promoters/primer).

Viewing technological challenges as opportunities - that is what we stand for as the ROWA GROUP. Guided by our philosophy, we develop quality materials for the polymer industry with dedication and passion, making it possible to design products for modern life more safely, efficiently and ecologically.

Whether commodities or special developments - the ROWA GROUP serves orders with outstanding speed and delivery reliability. We guarantee this with our first-class logistics: from filling in state-of-the-art facilities to the provision of finished goods in efficient high-bay warehouses and delivery by competent forwarding partners. All positions in the supply chain are perfectly interlinked. In combination with process-optimized production workflows, our customers receive a service that is unparalleled in terms of flexibility and cost-effectiveness - and goes far beyond delivery. Even after delivery, we are available to answer any technical questions. Our technicians are also happy to support the optimum use of our products on site if required.
