IMCD Deutschland GmbH
IMCD Advanced Materials
partners with world-class producers to develop innovative and sustainable solutions for a safer and healthier life.  
We distribute high-performance materials to our customers across regions. Our global network of expert teams are eager to collaborate with our clients active in 23 different end-markets within the Plastics Converting, Plastics Compounding and Composites industries. 

Our comprehensive product portfolio covers 18 different categories, allowing us to support our customers at different stages from product development to production optimisation. 

We are part of IMCD Group which is headquartered in Rotterdam, The Netherlands. IMCD is a leading global partner for the distribution and formulation of speciality chemicals and ingredients. A strong, innovative business partner and solutions provider for producers of consumer, industrial and durable goods. 

In 2024, with over 5,100 employees, IMCD realised revenues of EUR 4,728 million. IMCD N.V.’s shares are traded at Euronext Amsterdam (symbol: IMCD) and are included in the Dutch ESG AEX index, as one of 25 companies within the AEX and AMX indices demonstrating best ESG practices.

Learn more at our website: https://www.imcd.de/business-groups/advanced-materials
